<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20344222">为什么《射雕英雄传》里面的郭靖经常被演成傻子？如何分析郭靖的智商和情商？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="318066" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">我认为郭靖只是憨厚实诚，不然黄蓉会对他死心塌地、成吉思汗会那么喜欢他？</div>


</div>
